    <!-- Agreement Content -->
    <div class="agreement-container">
        <div class="agreement-card">
            <div class="section-title">
                <i class="fas fa-camera"></i>
                <h2>1. Media Release Authorization</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="agreement-content">
                <p>By participating in this event, you grant Council for the Restoration of Filipino Values, Inc. (CRFV) the irrevocable, perpetual, and worldwide rights to:</p>
                
                <ul>
                    <li>Capture photographs, video recordings, and audio recordings during the event (both in-person and virtual sessions)</li>
                    <li>Use, reproduce, modify, and distribute such media in all promotional materials, publications, social media, websites, and any other platforms</li>
                    <li>Use your name, likeness, and voice in connection with such media</li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <p><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> This authorization applies to all current and future media formats and platforms. No compensation or opt-out option is provided for media usage.</p>
                </div>
                
                <p>You understand that Council for the Restoration of Filipino Values, Inc. (CRFV) may use these materials for promotional, educational, and informational purposes without limitation.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="agreement-card">
            <div class="section-title">
                <i class="fas fa-undo-alt"></i>
                <h2>2. Item Return Policy</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="agreement-content">
                <p>Participants agree to return all provided items upon completion of the event. This includes but is not limited to:</p>
                
                <ul>
                    <li>Proximity cards or access devices</li>
                    <li>Training materials and equipment</li>
                    <li>Any other items provided by Council for the Restoration of Filipino Values, Inc. (CRFV) for the event</li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="warning-box">
                    <p><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Failure to return items by the end of the event will result in a fine of <strong>PHP 500.00 per item</strong>, payable within 15 days of the event's conclusion.</p>
                </div>
                
                <p>Items must be returned to the designated collection point at the event venue, or by prepaid mail if taken off-site.</p>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="agreement-card">
            <div class="section-title">
                <i class="fas fa-certificate"></i>
                <h2>3. Completion Certificate Requirements</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="agreement-content">
                <p>Council for the Restoration of Filipino Values, Inc. (CRFV) reserves the right to withhold the issuance of completion certificates if participants fail to meet the following requirements:</p>
                
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Full Attendance:</strong> Participants must attend 100% of mandatory sessions (verified via attendance tracking)</li>
                    <li><strong>Assessment Completion:</strong> Successful completion of all required assessments and assignments</li>
                    <li><strong>Item Return:</strong> Return of all provided items as specified in Section 2</li>
                    <li><strong>Code of Conduct:</strong> Adherence to all event rules and regulations</li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                <p><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Certificates are expected to be issued within 7 business days after the event, provided all requirements are completed. While we aim to meet this timeline, unforeseen delays may occur beyond the organizer's control.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="agreement-card">
            <div class="section-title">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                <h2>4. Data Privacy Compliance</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="agreement-content">
                <p>Council for the Restoration of Filipino Values, Inc. (CRFV) is committed to protecting your personal information in compliance with:</p>
                
                <ul>
                    <li>The <strong>Philippine Data Privacy Act (RA 10173)</strong></li>
                    <li>International data protection standards where applicable</li>
                </ul>
                
                <p>By agreeing to this participation agreement, you also consent to the terms of our Privacy Policy:</p>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <p><i class="fas fa-link"></i> <a href="/crfv/privacy-policy">HelloUniversity CRFV Privacy Policy</a></p>
                </div>
                
                <p>Your personal data will be used solely for event administration, communications, and the purposes outlined in this agreement.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="agreement-card">
            <div class="section-title">
                <i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i>
                <h2>5. General Terms</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="agreement-content">
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Governing Law:</strong> This agreement is governed by the laws of the Republic of the Philippines</li>
                    <li><strong>Amendments:</strong> Council for the Restoration of Filipino Values, Inc. (CRFV) reserves the right to update these terms. Changes will apply to future events</li>
                    <li><strong>Liability:</strong> Council for the Restoration of Filipino Values, Inc. (CRFV) is not liable for any loss or damage to personal property during the event</li>
                    <li><strong>Termination:</strong> Council for the Restoration of Filipino Values, Inc. (CRFV) reserves the right to remove participants who violate event policies</li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="warning-box">
                    <p><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Non-compliance with any terms of this agreement may result in exclusion from future Council for the Restoration of Filipino Values, Inc. (CRFV) events.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

